S.FORM: Didier Burkhalter 4 a bulad 17 a demiad, Didier Burkhalter, u misingkiway. 1960 a mihcaan nalecuhan. u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung ) nu Switzerland ayza sa ci Didier Burkhalter, micakat a demiad sa i 2012 a mihcaan 1 a bulad 1 a demiad. malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan u piazihan tu sulit nu ayzaay a tabakiay a mikeliday asaca angangan nu kanatal atu sefu(List of current heads of state and government)
